Variables
--------

Variables are containers for storing data values

Datatypes
----------
Primitive data type
Non-Primitive data type

Primitive data type - 8 types

byte - 8bits - 1byte - 2^8 = 256 (-128 to 127)
short -2 bytes - 2^16 = 65536 (-32768 to 32767)
int - 4 bytes - 2^32 = 4294967296 (
long - 8 bytes - 2^64

float - 4 bytes
double - 8 bytes

char - 2 bytes
boolean - 1 bit



JRE - Java Runtime Envi
JDK - Java Dev Kit
JVM - Java Virtual Machine


